person.bio: A motivated entrepreneur, background in sports, passionate to find opportunities to create impact businesses and initiatives fitting the much-needed era of balance. I strongly believe that communities working together can make us happier while helping our unique and beautiful planet to thrive. I am delighted to wake up every morning to design, develop, and promote technological tools to empower communities. Happy to be part of this alliance to fulfill this mutual vision towards a better world in which vibrant communities empower people!
